define cell NeuralProgenitorCell from StemCell
    mechanisms:
        NPCDivide(duration: 100) from Divide
            parameters: (_, _)
            => on condition set NPCDivideCondition

        mutual exclusive
            NPCToRGCDifferentiate(duration: 100) from Differentiate
                parameters: (RadialGliaCell)
                => on NPCDifferentiateCondition with probability: Gaussian(NPCF, [3.25, 0.59])
                -| all

            NPCToBPCDifferentiate(duration: 100) from Differentiate
                parameters: (BasalProgenitorCell)
                => on NPCDifferentiateCondition with probability: Gaussian(NPCF, [3.25, 0.59])
                -| all

        -> cyclic NPCFSpread(duration: 100) from SignalSpread
            parameters: (NPCF)
            -| on condition set NPCDivideCondition

        NPCApoptize(duration: 100) from Apoptize
            => on NPCApoptizeCondition
            -| all

    conditions:
        NPCApoptizeCondition
            receptor 5HT2a is activate
            mechanism NPCFSpread is active
            molecule NSCF is in [0, 0,01)

        NPCDivideCondition
            molecule NSCF is in (0.05, infinity)

        NPCDifferentiateCondition
            molecule NSCF is in [4.15, infinity)
            molecule NSCF is in [0, 0.9)